title: David Sedaris Returns
description:
Writer David Sedaris feels fantastic about being Conan O’Brien’s friend.


 

David and Conan sit down together once more to discuss David’s new book Happy-Go-Lucky, the importance of dressing up, being alone in Alaska, and family dysfunction. Later, Conan considers the possibility of performing in hospital delivery rooms as he and his team Review the Reviewers.


 


 


 

Got a question for Conan? Call our voicemail: (323) 451-2821.


 

For Conan videos, tour dates and more visit TeamCoco.com.
